"label":"event"},{"source":"recuPyUbklXqyiqp4","target":"recAyNphNXcFdeBdv","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recSuGD8w5qOWh6W5","ref":"Gen.29.1","text":"Then Jacob went on his journey, and came into the land of the people of the east."},{"id":"recFiFS4aiImqo4Fw","ref":"Gen.29.2","text":"And he looked, and behold a well in the field, and, lo, there were three flocks of sheep lying by it; for out of that well they watered the flocks: and a great stone was upon the well’s mouth."},{"id":"recZnweRqqcmAakdJ","ref":"Gen.29.3","text":"And thither were all the flocks gathered: and they rolled the stone from the well’s mouth, and watered the sheep, and put the stone again upon the well’s mouth in his place."},{"id":"recsbs1cuZQPBXmFX","ref":"Gen.29.4","text":"And Jacob said unto them, My brethren, whence be ye? And they said, Of Haran are we."},{"id":"recIoYdGQrw1M1h46","ref":"Gen.29.5","text":"And he said unto them, Know ye Laban the son of Nahor? And they said, We know him."},{"id":"recfR90djuCUJFpFi","ref":"Gen.29.6","text":"And he said unto them, Is he well? And they said, He is well: and, behold, Rachel his daughter cometh with the sheep."},{"id":"recsAhTv5YvAHHQGL","ref":"Gen.29.7","text":"And he said, Lo, it is yet high day, neither is it time that the cattle should be gathered together: water ye the sheep, and go and feed them."},{"id":"recjwHeTwncPPEocz","ref":"Gen.29.8","text":"And they said, We cannot, until all the flocks be gathered together, and till they roll the stone from the well’s mouth; then we water the sheep."}]}
